{"tid":2517344,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"脫北者參選！ 代表英國保守黨角逐曼市議席  早於6.13已聲援港人","createTime":"2021-05-05T09:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T09:15:47.000Z","uid":35519,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4ef4765aa7c667139e4a3fc8f82cb06e436ada44","tid":2517344,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:10:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">脫北者參選！<br />\n代表英國保守黨角逐曼市議席 <br />\n早於6.13起已聲援港人</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSTQd1NfzKowKShMojV8kYcQyKgZFJ5GnGyHekDjrCnjW?filename=FzRSycc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFzRSycc.jpg&h=6ca4d9e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新聞報道：<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/news/article/37/734071\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F37%2F734071&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnzUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=67c95eb0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F37%2F734071&h=96481ed6\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/news/article/37/734071</a><br />\n<br />\n【有線新聞】因為疫情延遲近一年的英國地方選舉，會在周四舉行。代表保守黨角逐曼徹斯特地方議席的朴智賢受到矚目。她是英國第一個出來參選的變節北韓人，稱要為所有無發言權的人發聲。<br />\n<br />\n現年52歲的朴智賢，在北韓咸鏡北道的山區長大，90年代經歷北韓大飢荒。1998年，聽從父親囑咐，帶着弟弟逃到中國，打算過好生活。<br />\n<br />\n怎料朴智賢與弟弟失散，她被販賣至黑龍江給農民做妻子和強迫工作。<br />\n<br />\n她憶述：「買我的人說，我花錢買你，現在你必須做我叫你做的事。如果你絲毫不服從，我可以舉報你，即使殺了你，沒人會說甚麼，沒人會知你發生甚麼事。」<br />\n<br />\n朴智賢在中國生活到第6年後被捕、被遣返北韓，更被判入勞改營，受到守衛毒打，從凌晨4時半工作到半夜。<br />\n<br />\n她說：「我們工作比動物更辛勞，你可以說整個北韓是一個大監獄。」<br />\n<br />\n做了數個月苦工，朴智賢腳部傷口出現壞疽，垂死之際被趕出勞改營。她由北韓返回中國，再輾轉逃至蒙古，其間結識了現任丈夫。2007年透過一位韓裔牧師協助與聯合國聯繫，翌年舉家移居英格蘭中部伯里展開新生活。<br />\n<br />\n朴智賢說跟北韓相比，英國生活簡直是天堂。保守黨對家庭價值觀和個人自由的重視吸引了她入黨，展開從政之路。<br />\n<br />\n朴智賢積極為人權問題發聲，致力協助北韓難民適應英國生活。促請中國不要遣返北韓難民、聲援香港爭取自由。<br />\n<br />\n新型肺炎疫情爆發，朴智賢捐贈物資給當地護老院，見證長者與家人生離死別的故事，她感同身受。又希望為保守黨從這個自由民主黨的大本營贏得議席，回饋曾經幫助過她的社區。"},{"pid":"874b09992f047ff232b6feac748ba81c9096e5cf","tid":2517344,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:11:41.000Z","msg":"Twitter摘錄<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">2019年6月13日&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n已聲援撐港人</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/JihyunPark7/status/1139070348446576640\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJihyunPark7%2Fstatus%2F1139070348446576640&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnzUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=7649a8cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJihyunPark7%2Fstatus%2F1139070348446576640&h=07486eb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/JihyunPark7/status/1139070348446576640</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">2019年6月25日&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n隻身到中國駐英大使館 抗議反送中惡法</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/JihyunPark7/status/1143233711799963648\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJihyunPark7%2Fstatus%2F1143233711799963648&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnzUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=0652e127\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJihyunPark7%2Fstatus%2F1143233711799963648&h=bd541ab4\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/JihyunPark7/status/1143233711799963648</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">2019年8月14日&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n引用George Orwell名言，關注爆眼少女 </span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/JihyunPark7/status/1161616920002662400\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJihyunPark7%2Fstatus%2F1161616920002662400&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnzUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=40fbb9ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJihyunPark7%2Fstatus%2F1161616920002662400&h=1960d389\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/JihyunPark7/status/1161616920002662400</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>2020年5月&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nTwitter上分享「天滅中共」</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/JihyunPark7/status/1264824361409748992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJihyunPark7%2Fstatus%2F1264824361409748992&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnzUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=e42fdf03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJihyunPark7%2Fstatus%2F1264824361409748992&h=2399aeea\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/JihyunPark7/status/1264824361409748992</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">2020年12月&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n分享張展案時，直指#CCPVirus</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/JihyunPark7/status/1343519205937836033\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJihyunPark7%2Fstatus%2F1343519205937836033&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnzUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=3b534ab7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJihyunPark7%2Fstatus%2F1343519205937836033&h=5d8c3888\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/JihyunPark7/status/1343519205937836033</a>"},{"pid":"3bd69b6b6b3db99bd240df71e0b101a661a36508","tid":2517344,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:15:47.000Z","msg":"台灣蘋果日報專訪<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SG04JthbQWM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSG04JthbQWM&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnzUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=172f1f8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SG04JthbQWM</a>"}]}